Responsive Websites using Grid 
As the name suggests, it is used to make the websites responsive

Used Properties in Responsive Grid Design

grid-template-column: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(100px, 150px))

minmax -> represents the size of cards/elements/div/container 
100px -> min size 
150px -> max size


Grid Template Areas
This is also used to create layouts very easiy

Properties:

#header{
    grid-area: header;
}

grid-template-areas: 
    "header header header"
    "sidebar content1 content1"
    "sidebar content2 content3"
    "footer footer footer"
;